            <div type="apparatus" resp="#martaf">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note>Text based on photographs. The Greek fragment has not been observed: Mommsen was the last editor to observe it.</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="line 2"><note>Mommsen, Kaibel: ann(os); Korhonen: ann(is)</note></app>
                    <app loc="line 3"><note>Mommsen read Μ·ΜΑΡΥΛΜ·ΕΖ[---]. On the surviving fragment (a) are visible the top of an Α followed by a lunate Ε and the top of a Ζ.</note></app>
                </listApp>
